      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Nor Turistväg - Atlanterhavsvegen</name>
        <description><![CDATA[“The road across the sea” is the iconic experience with bridges that arch between the islets and reefs along the rough Hustadvika Bay.<br><br>Atlanterhavsvegen - the Atlantic Road - is a visual delight as it curves elegantly from islet to islet over its seven bridges. Nature and modern engineering meet and create this highly unique driving experience.<br><br>The trip takes you from the fertile cultural landscape of the coast across moorland to bare crags along the weather-beaten, open bay of Hustadvika. Take time to watch the sun disappearing below the horizon from here. Atlanterhavsvegen has been described as the world’s most beautiful drive.]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#line-FF5252-3000</styleUrl>
        <LineString>
